# PingFederate SSO configuration - Manual approach
OIDCProviderIssuer https://pingfederate.yourbank.com
OIDCProviderAuthorizationEndpoint https://pingfederate.yourbank.com/as/authorization.oauth2
OIDCProviderTokenEndpoint https://pingfederate.yourbank.com/as/token.oauth2
OIDCProviderUserInfoEndpoint https://pingfederate.yourbank.com/idp/userinfo.openid
OIDCProviderJwksUri https://pingfederate.yourbank.com/.well-known/jwks.json

# Client configuration
OIDCClientID your_client_id
OIDCClientSecret your_client_secret
OIDCRedirectURI https://api.bank.com/jwt-callback
OIDCCryptoPassphrase some-random-secure-passphrase

# Session settings
OIDCSessionInactivityTimeout 3600
OIDCSessionMaxDuration 28800

# Scope and claims
OIDCScope "openid email profile"
OIDCRemoteUserClaim sub
OIDCResponseType "id_token token"

# SSL and token handling
OIDCSSLValidateServer On
OIDCPassIDTokenAs claims
OIDCPassClaimsAs environment
OIDCPassRefreshToken On
